      image_prompt: `Painterly editorial illustration, slightly satirical, warm muted tones with gold and deep red accents. Academic setting. No text in image. Style: New Yorker cartoon meets university portrait gallery.\n\nScene: A formal press release resting on an ornate wooden desk; beside it, an elaborate academic seal stamp and an inkpad; in the background, tall windows overlook an empty auditorium; no person is visible, only the document, the stamp, and the silence.\nMood: institutional, slightly ominous.\nNo text, no logos, no real people.`,
